QUANTUM CELLULAR AUTOMATA · node QCA · QCA · QUANTUM CELLULAR AUTOMATA · METAXÝ · the between · classical CA ⇄ the quantum frontier · UD0 / METAXÝ

universe of origin : the bridge between classical cellular automata and the quantum frontier
seal               : Take the grid of local rules that makes a Game of Life — and give each cell a quantum state. You get a quantum cellular automaton: provably able to compute anything a quantum computer can, buildable in quantum-dot hardware, and able to mend a quantum computer's errors. The clean middle between the classical automata and the quantum frontier.
